eplyTime":"2018-03-22T05:02:47.000Z","msg":"無著反光衣就可以咁樣被撞死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T05:40:41.000Z","msg":"路政署提提你<br />\n<br />\n高能見度衣服<br />\r4.52 所有在車路或其附近工作的人員，為本身的安全起見，須經常穿著能見度高，並有反光條紋或斑紋的衣服，讓駕駛人士容易看見。根據道路交通(快速公路)規例(第 374Q 章)， 任何快速公路工程人員在快速公路任何部分步行時，均須穿著屬路政署署長認可類型的反光 外衣。如有需要，工程人員應穿著反光褲，使其更明顯易見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hyd.gov.hk/tc/publications_and_publicity/publications/technical_document/code_of_practice/doc/COP_201712.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hyd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublications_and_publicity%2Fpublications%2Ftechnical_document%2Fcode_of_practice%2Fdoc%2FCOP_201712.pdf&d=p9Oj975Ubuqw252xh3w5Li7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=04be7279\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hyd.gov.hk/tc/publications_and_publicity/publications/technical_document/code_of_practice/doc/COP_201712.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然東九龍走廊唔算快速公路，但都行成70，唔著反光衣喺上面四圍行，係抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"910d1df09c7e4a8b5e8a7944d36ad56fc006e7d8","tid":601131,"uid":16193,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"180f4d454618fcce74051ad079473a2cb4b35ceb","tid":601131,"uid":171107,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"336cb9cff4d85097a6bbce5f2027e3d550325ab1","tid":601131,"uid":16193,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T05:02:47.000Z","msg":"無著反光衣就可以咁樣被撞死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T05:26:32.000Z","msg":"九唔搭八，宜家係講緊條差佬唔著反光衣＞搞到司機睇佢唔到＞司機撞左埋去<br />\n佢唔著反光衣就自己害死自己 仲要害埋人，咪撚咩事都左膠膠上腦啦on9"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T05:42:16.000Z","msg":"有雪糕筒、電筒有光，仲有街燈，乜都睇唔到？<